-- DEPENDENCIES --
* php-oauth (http://code.google.com/p/oauth/)

        ==> Fedora Package (php-oauth)
                http://admin.fedoraproject.org/updates/php-oauth

        ==> Debian Package (liboauth-php)

        NOTE JUST FOR PACKAGE MAINTAINERS:
        When using the SVN version the php-oauth library is included
        as an external dependency and automatically fetched and used.
        Modify the configuration file to use the system-wide version.

        # Fedora
        $config['oauth_lib_dir'] = '/usr/share/php/oauth'

        # Debian
        $config['oauth_lib_dir'] = '/usr/share/php'

